{"id":530460,"date":[{"year":1973,"month":9,"day":10}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"140","ytitle":"","mtitle":"十大光辉照炉台","ftitle":"","authors":["谷亨利"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上钢一厂　谷亨利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日照钢城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉前热腾腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火闪耀舞红绸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢包排成彩练灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼钢工炉前庆十大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不胸中热浪滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗火红的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人火辣的劲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥舞长钎力千钧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒把热汗钢万吨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢，是优质的钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人，是革命的人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十大光辉照炉台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢人铁马喊前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉炉吐情迎朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凯歌声声飞北京。"}]}